Do you know of any novelizations of old games?<br />I'm not talking about general stories with Mario, Mega Man or whoever in it, but about stories that are actually a novelization conversion of a specific game's plot.<br />Like if there was a book that tells the story of Trevor Belmont how he sets out to defeat Dracula and meets Alucard, Sypha and Grant on the way. That's what I'm looking for.<br />On the other hand, a story about how Trevor and Sypha, who are now married, fight a group of vampires that try to kill them because they defeated Dracula three years ago, that's not what I want.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6156">DRW</a> — Thu Oct 17, 2013 3:55 pm</p><hr />
